data.name: Flavorchem & Orchidia Fragrances
data.description:
Flavorchem and Orchidia Fragrances specializes in the creation and manufacturing of flavor, fragrance, and ingredient solutions. Established in 1971, we are a privately held business partnering with brands well recognized throughout the world. We strive to provide our customers with the highest-quality products, superior service, and innovative solutions. Today we manufacture over 5,000 flavors, fragrances, and private-label food products annually.

We believe in making investments that enhance our capabilities to better serve our customers. We have robust Quality, R&D, Regulatory, Marketing, and Manufacturing capabilities and capacities to provide our customers with scale to grow their business.

Our Services & Capabilities Include

  • Pilot Thermal Processing
  • Dedicated Sensory Department & Testing Services
  • Product Development
  • Flavor & Fragrance Training
  • Quality & Regulatory Support
  • Packaging Capabilities 
  • And More!

We create highly-custom taste and sensory experiences driving product innovation by working closely to support your application needs. From pure vanilla bean and organic ingredients to natural fragrances and oils, our vast flavor and fragrance portfolio encompasses a range of segments including bakery, beverage, beauty, and personal care.

Browse our online storefront to discover the best in flavor and fragrance innovation.

data.description: Orchidia Fragrances Cannabis-Inspired Terpenes Fragrence (ORC1901523) is an herbaceous blend that highlights the terpenes found in cannabis but is sourced from other botanicals. It has transparent citrus top notes infused with lavender, sappy pine, warming pepper, and amber for that foggy forest feel.

data.name: Orchidia Fragrances Paradise Sunrise (ORC1800590)
data.description: Orchidia Fragrances Joy #1 Fragrance (ORC1800590) is a clear yellow to golden yellow liquid, which has joyful notes of fizzy mandarin and juicy oranges wash over a heart of lush pikake jasmine and ripened raspberry, winding to a gentle base of musk and amber.

data.name: Orchidia Fragrances Aquarius Fragrance (PC) (ORC2301220)
data.description: Orchidia Fragrances Aquarius Fragrance (PC) (ORC2301220) is a liquid with an appearance ranging from clear colorless to pale yellow. It is characterized by the organoleptic properties of green citrus marine. This fragrance is designed for use in fragrances and perfume applications within the personal care market, particularly in the beauty and care segment. It comes with the labeling claim of being allergen-free.

data.name: Flavorchem Chocolate Whiskey Type Flavor NAT (17.4030)
data.description: Flavorchem Chocolate Whiskey Type Flavor NAT (17.4030) is an exclusive flavor inspired by the current flavor trends in the coffee industry. It is presented as a dark brown liquid with a chocolate whiskey-like flavor and odor. This flavor is derived from natural sources and is non-GMO, allergen-free, and vegan. It is a premium flavor that can be used to create new menu ideas and drive consumer interest in a wide range of food and beverage applications.

data.name: Orchidia Fragrances Peony Mimosa (ORC1800562)
data.description: Orchidia Fragrances Gratitude #2 Fragrance (ORC1800562) is a clear, pale to golden yellow liquid that has playful hints of lemon and lime. It refreshes the heart with juicy melon, enveloped by a garden of peony and stargazer lily. The fragrance rests on a delicate base of orange blossom and mimosa.

data.name: Flavorchem Lime Extract (Natural) (52.075)
data.description: Flavorchem Lime Extract (Natural) (52.075) is a clear, colorless to pale yellow liquid with a lime-like flavor and odor. It has juicy and zesty notes with hints of pine and terpenic notes. The suggested usage for this extract is 0.10%. It is also suitable for other partially water-soluble applications.

data.name: Orchidia Fragrances Spatopia (Candles) (ORC2202833)
data.description: Orchidia Fragrances Spatopia (Candles) (ORC2202833) is a fragrance ingredient that appears as a clear, colorless to pale yellow liquid with a floral, green, and citrus-like flavor and odor. It is generally used as an aromatic ingredient in the manufacture of candles.

data.name: Flavorchem Pear Elderflower Flavouring (UF07441)
data.description: Flavorchem Pear Elderflower Flavouring (UF07441) is a liquid food ingredient that serves as a flavoring agent. It imparts both aroma and flavor, combining the delicate tastes of pear and elderflower. This flavoring is derived from natural origins and belongs to both fruit and herb flavor families. Classified under mixed flavoring agents, it is a versatile addition to a wide range of culinary applications.

data.name: Flavorchem Masking Powder, NAT. (GMOF EU) (29.005GM)
data.description: Flavorchem Masking Powder, NAT. (GMOF EU) (29.005GM) is a masking agent in powder form that adds sweetness, masks off-notes, and can be labeled as a natural flavor. Its suggested use level starts at 0.05 - 0.10% and can be adjusted as desired.

data.name: Flavorchem & Orchidia Fragrances
data.description:
Flavorchem and Orchidia Fragrances specializes in the creation and manufacturing of flavor, fragrance, and ingredient solutions. Established in 1971, we are a privately held business partnering with brands well recognized throughout the world. We strive to provide our customers with the highest-quality products, superior service, and innovative solutions. Today we manufacture over 5,000 flavors, fragrances, and private-label food products annually.

We believe in making investments that enhance our capabilities to better serve our customers. We have robust Quality, R&D, Regulatory, Marketing, and Manufacturing capabilities and capacities to provide our customers with scale to grow their business.

Our Services & Capabilities Include

  • Pilot Thermal Processing
  • Dedicated Sensory Department & Testing Services
  • Product Development
  • Flavor & Fragrance Training
  • Quality & Regulatory Support
  • Packaging Capabilities 
  • And More!

We create highly-custom taste and sensory experiences driving product innovation by working closely to support your application needs. From pure vanilla bean and organic ingredients to natural fragrances and oils, our vast flavor and fragrance portfolio encompasses a range of segments including bakery, beverage, beauty, and personal care.

Browse our online storefront to discover the best in flavor and fragrance innovation.
